<h1 class="h3 mb-3 font-weight-normal"><center><strong>Benutzerkonto erstellen</strong></center></h1>
<center><img src="/static/images/alexa_connect_icons/alexa-connect.png"></center>
<br/>
<div class="input-group mb-3">
    <div class="input-group-prepend">
        <span class="input-group-text" style="width: 50px;" id="basic-addon2" disabled><span class="iconify" data-icon="bx:bxs-user" data-width="25" data-height="25"></span></span>
    </div>
    <input type="text" id="username" name="username" style="text-transform: lowercase;" pattern="^[a-z0-9]{5,15}$" class="form-control" autocapitalize="none" required autofocus title="Benutzername" autocomplete="username">
</div>
<p><small id="usernameHelpBlock" class="form-text text-muted">Muss in Kleinbuchstaben geschrieben werden, 5-15 Zeichen einschließlich a-z und 0-9.</small></p>
<div class="input-group mb-3">
    <div class="input-group-prepend">
        <span class="input-group-text" style="width: 50px;" id="basic-addon2" disabled><span class="iconify" data-icon="heroicons-solid:mail" data-width="25" data-height="25"></span></span>
    </div>
    <input type="email" id="email" class="form-control" required title="E-Mail Adresse">
</div>
<p><small id="emailHelpBlock" class="form-text text-muted">Sie müssen Ihre E-Mail-Adresse bestätigen.</small></p>
